QuestData.Title: Food From Below
QuestData.Description: Supplies are running low here in camp, $n. We have recently learned that the cellblock just southwest of here has a number of rations remaining from years of use. We need you to gather as many of those as you can and bring them back to camp.$B$BOne more thing, the entire cellblock is overrun with prisoners so be careful.
QuestData.LogDescription: You have been asked to recover 12 Cellblock Rations from The Hole, just southwest of Baradin Hold.
